---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="D0 — Agent Meets Money"
  description="D0 turns any AI into a trading desk. 155 tools, real PnL. If you can chat, you can trade."
>

<!-- ═══ HERO ═══ -->
<section class="lp-hero">
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-badge"><span class="badge-dot"></span><span data-i18n="lp.heroBadge">SUPER D0 · LIVE</span></div>
    <h1 class="hero-headline"><span class="hero-slogan">Agent Meets Money.</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-hook" data-i18n="lp.heroHook">If you can chat, you can trade.</p>
    <p class="hero-sub" data-i18n="lp.heroSub">D0 is an AI trading agent you talk to. Ask a question — it fires 155 tools and gives you a trade setup. Say "execute" — it places the order. No apps. Just conversation.</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="https://t.me/DonutD0Bot" target="_blank" class="btn-primary" data-i18n="lp.heroCta1">Talk to D0 on Telegram →</a>
      <a href="#trades" class="btn-ghost" data-i18n="lp.heroCta2">See real trades ↓</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ PNL MARQUEE ═══ -->
<section class="lp-trades" id="trades">
  <div class="trades-inner">
    <div class="section-label" data-i18n="lp.tradesLabel">WHAT D0 TRADERS ARE DOING</div>
    <h2 class="trades-title" data-i18n="lp.tradesTitle">Real scenarios. Real PnL.</h2>
    <p class="trades-disclaimer" data-i18n="lp.tradesDisclaimer">Simulated scenarios for illustration only. Past performance is not indicative of future results. Not financial advice.</p>

    <div class="marquee-wrap" aria-hidden="true">
      <!-- Row 1: scrolls left. Must clone exactly 1× for seamless loop -->
      <div class="marquee-row" id="marqueeRow1">
        <div class="marquee-track">
          <div class="m-card">
            <div class="mc-top"><span class="mc-avatar" style="--av-bg:#FF6B6B">CZ</span><span class="mc-user">CryptoZen</span><span class="mc-type long">LONG BTC</span></div>
            <div class="mc-pnl green">+$2,340</div>
            <div class="mc-desc" data-i18n="lp.mq1">Fed day 3x leverage play, cut at +4.2%</div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-card">
            <div class="mc-top"><span class="mc-avatar" style="--av-bg:#4ECDC4">DW</span><span class="mc-user">DegenWhale</span><span class="mc-type arb">ARB</span></div>
            <div class="mc-pnl green">+$340<small>/day</small></div>
            <div class="mc-desc" data-i18n="lp.mq2">Funding rate 0.12% — delta-neutral hedge</div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-card featured">
            <div class="mc-top"><span class="mc-avatar" style="--av-bg:#E8B84E">AP</span><span class="mc-user">AutoPilot</span><span class="mc-type auto">30D AUTO</span></div>
            <div class="mc-pnl gold">+$4,200</div>
            <div class="mc-desc" data-i18n="lp.mq3">23 trades · 67% WR · Sharpe 1.4</div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-card">
            <div class="mc-top"><span class="mc-avatar" style="--av-bg:#A78BFA">MH</span><span class="mc-user">MemeHunter</span><span class="mc-type long">LONG BONK</span></div>
            <div class="mc-pnl green">+29%</div>
            <div class="mc-desc" data-i18n="lp.mq4">Social spike 340% → rug check clean → snipe</div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-card">
            <div class="mc-top"><span class="mc-avatar" style="--av-bg:#F97316">LQ</span><span class="mc-user">LiqHunter</span><span class="mc-type short">SHORT BTC</span></div>
            <div class="mc-pnl green">+18%</div>
            <div class="mc-desc" data-i18n="lp.mq5">$420M longs clustered — cascade triggered</div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-card">
            <div class="mc-top"><span class="mc-avatar" style="--av-bg:#06B6D4">YF</span><span class="mc-user">YieldFarmer</span><span class="mc-type arb">YIELD</span></div>
            <div class="mc-pnl gold">+$180<small>/mo</small></div>
            <div class="mc-desc" data-i18n="lp.mq6">Drift → Kamino auto-rotation, 14.2% APY</div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-card">
            <div class="mc-top"><span class="mc-avatar" style="--av-bg:#EC4899">SS</span><span class="mc-user">ScalpStar</span><span class="mc-type long">LONG ETH</span></div>
            <div class="mc-pnl green">+$870</div>
            <div class="mc-desc" data-i18n="lp.mq7">RSI oversold bounce, 15min chart scalp</div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-card">
            <div class="mc-top"><span class="mc-avatar" style="--av-bg:#10B981">WM</span><span class="mc-user">WhaleMode</span><span class="mc-type long">LONG SOL</span></div>
            <div class="mc-pnl green">+42%</div>
            <div class="mc-desc" data-i18n="lp.mq8">Whale wallet tracking → followed accumulation</div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-card">
            <div class="mc-top"><span class="mc-avatar" style="--av-bg:#8B5CF6">QS</span><span class="mc-user">QuantSage</span><span class="mc-type auto">ALGO</span></div>
            <div class="mc-pnl green">+$1,560</div>
            <div class="mc-desc" data-i18n="lp.mq9">Bollinger squeeze breakout strategy backtest → live</div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-card">
            <div class="mc-top"><span class="mc-avatar" style="--av-bg:#F59E0B">PM</span><span class="mc-user">PolyMax</span><span class="mc-type arb">PREDICT</span></div>
            <div class="mc-pnl green">+$620</div>
            <div class="mc-desc" data-i18n="lp.mq10">Polymarket ETF approval odds 72% → bought YES</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Row 2: scrolls right -->
      <div class="marquee-row reverse" id="marqueeRow2">
        <div class="marquee-track">
          <div class="m-card">
            <div class="mc-top"><span class="mc-avatar" style="--av-bg:#EF4444">BR</span><span class="mc-user">BearRekt</span><span class="mc-type short">SHORT ETH</span></div>
            <div class="mc-pnl green">+$1,100</div>
            <div class="mc-desc" data-i18n="lp.mq11">Funding rate spike + OI divergence → short setup</div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-card">
            <div class="mc-top"><span class="mc-avatar" style="--av-bg:#14B8A6">AF</span><span class="mc-user">ApeFirst</span><span class="mc-type long">LONG WIF</span></div>
            <div class="mc-pnl green">+67%</div>
            <div class="mc-desc" data-i18n="lp.mq12">Social volume explosion → D0 rug check passed</div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-card">
            <div class="mc-top"><span class="mc-avatar" style="--av-bg:#6366F1">NK</span><span class="mc-user">NightKing</span><span class="mc-type auto">30D AUTO</span></div>
            <div class="mc-pnl gold">+$3,800</div>
            <div class="mc-desc" data-i18n="lp.mq13">Regime-aware autopilot, 19 trades, max DD -4.1%</div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-card">
            <div class="mc-top"><span class="mc-avatar" style="--av-bg:#D946EF">GG</span><span class="mc-user">GigaGains</span><span class="mc-type long">LONG AVAX</span></div>
            <div class="mc-pnl green">+$2,900</div>
            <div class="mc-desc" data-i18n="lp.mq14">On-chain TVL surge 48hr before breakout</div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-card">
            <div class="mc-top"><span class="mc-avatar" style="--av-bg:#0EA5E9">RB</span><span class="mc-user">RatioBot</span><span class="mc-type arb">ARB</span></div>
            <div class="mc-pnl green">+$460<small>/day</small></div>
            <div class="mc-desc" data-i18n="lp.mq15">CEX vs DEX price gap arb, automated rebalance</div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-card">
            <div class="mc-top"><span class="mc-avatar" style="--av-bg:#84CC16">DX</span><span class="mc-user">DeFiMax</span><span class="mc-type arb">YIELD</span></div>
            <div class="mc-pnl gold">+$520<small>/mo</small></div>
            <div class="mc-desc" data-i18n="lp.mq16">3-protocol yield rotation, auto-compound</div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-card">
            <div class="mc-top"><span class="mc-avatar" style="--av-bg:#F43F5E">MC</span><span class="mc-user">MacroCalls</span><span class="mc-type long">LONG BTC</span></div>
            <div class="mc-pnl green">+$5,200</div>
            <div class="mc-desc" data-i18n="lp.mq17">CPI below consensus + whale inflow → positioned for rally</div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-card">
            <div class="mc-top"><span class="mc-avatar" style="--av-bg:#22D3EE">SN</span><span class="mc-user">SniperNFT</span><span class="mc-type long">LONG ONDO</span></div>
            <div class="mc-pnl green">+34%</div>
            <div class="mc-desc" data-i18n="lp.mq18">RWA narrative + Blackrock filing = breakout</div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-card">
            <div class="mc-top"><span class="mc-avatar" style="--av-bg:#A3E635">HL</span><span class="mc-user">HyperLad</span><span class="mc-type short">SHORT DOGE</span></div>
            <div class="mc-pnl green">+$780</div>
            <div class="mc-desc" data-i18n="lp.mq19">Elon tweet faded, funding rate 0.15% → mean revert</div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-card">
            <div class="mc-top"><span class="mc-avatar" style="--av-bg:#FB923C">GR</span><span class="mc-user">GridRunner</span><span class="mc-type auto">GRID</span></div>
            <div class="mc-pnl gold">+$290<small>/wk</small></div>
            <div class="mc-desc" data-i18n="lp.mq20">Range-bound ETH grid bot, 82 fills in 7 days</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ TRADE STORIES ═══ -->
<section class="lp-stories scroll-reveal">
  <div class="stories-inner">
    <div class="section-label" data-i18n="lp.storiesLabel">DEEP DIVES</div>
    <h2 class="stories-headline" data-i18n="lp.storiesTitle">How D0 traders actually make money</h2>

    <div class="stories-grid">
      <div class="story-card">
        <div class="sc-header">
          <span class="sc-type" data-i18n="lp.t1Type">FUNDING RATE ARB</span>
          <span class="sc-time">⏱ 45s</span>
        </div>
        <p class="sc-story" data-i18n="lp.t1Story">BTC funding rate spiked to 0.12% — 4x normal. D0 opened a delta-neutral hedge: long spot + short perps. Collects the rate premium every 8 hours while staying market-neutral.</p>
        <div class="sc-pnl-block green">
          <div class="sc-pnl">+$340<span class="sc-pnl-unit">/day</span></div>
          <div class="sc-pnl-sub" data-i18n="lp.t1PnlSub">passive income · zero directional risk</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-tools"><span>d0 fundingrate BTC</span><span>d0 perps:order</span><span>d0 swap</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="story-card">
        <div class="sc-header">
          <span class="sc-type" data-i18n="lp.t2Type">FED DAY TRADE</span>
          <span class="sc-time">⏱ 2min</span>
        </div>
        <p class="sc-story" data-i18n="lp.t2Story">FOMC day. D0 pre-scanned: Fear & Greed at 22, CME FedWatch showing 78% rate cut probability, whales accumulating. Positioned long BTC 3x before the announcement. Cut at +4.2% move.</p>
        <div class="sc-pnl-block green">
          <div class="sc-pnl">+$2,100</div>
          <div class="sc-pnl-sub" data-i18n="lp.t2PnlSub">4.2% move captured · 3x leverage · stop-loss never hit</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-tools"><span>d0 feargreed</span><span>d0 macro</span><span>d0 whale-monitor</span><span>d0 perps:order</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="story-card featured">
        <div class="sc-header">
          <span class="sc-type" data-i18n="lp.t3Type">30-DAY AUTOPILOT</span>
          <span class="sc-time">📅 30 days</span>
        </div>
        <p class="sc-story" data-i18n="lp.t3Story">One trader let D0 run for a month with Guardrails active. D0 executed 23 trades autonomously — entries based on regime detection, exits based on trailing stops. 2% max loss per trade enforced.</p>
        <div class="sc-pnl-block gold">
          <div class="sc-pnl">+$4,200</div>
          <div class="sc-pnl-sub" data-i18n="lp.t3PnlSub">23 trades · 67% win rate · Sharpe 1.4 · max DD -6.2%</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-tools"><span>d0 regime</span><span>d0 signal-compress</span><span>d0 perps:order</span><span>d0 guardrail</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="story-card">
        <div class="sc-header">
          <span class="sc-type" data-i18n="lp.t4Type">MEME ALPHA SNIPE</span>
          <span class="sc-time">⏱ 30s</span>
        </div>
        <p class="sc-story" data-i18n="lp.t4Story">D0 detected $BONK Twitter mention volume spike 340% in 2 hours. Ran rug check: LP locked 180 days, top 10 hold 12%, deployer clean. Bought at $0.024. Set TP at $0.031. Hit in 6 hours.</p>
        <div class="sc-pnl-block green">
          <div class="sc-pnl">+29%</div>
          <div class="sc-pnl-sub" data-i18n="lp.t4PnlSub">$1,820 profit · social signal → safety check → execute · 6hr hold</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-tools"><span>d0 trending</span><span>d0 rugcheck</span><span>d0 swap</span><span>d0 limit</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="story-card">
        <div class="sc-header">
          <span class="sc-type" data-i18n="lp.t5Type">LIQUIDATION CASCADE</span>
          <span class="sc-time">⏱ 90s</span>
        </div>
        <p class="sc-story" data-i18n="lp.t5Story">D0 flagged: $420M in BTC longs clustered at 5x-10x leverage, liquidation zone at $81,200. Funding rate 0.09% and rising. Opened short with tight stop. Price swept longs — cascade triggered.</p>
        <div class="sc-pnl-block green">
          <div class="sc-pnl">+18%</div>
          <div class="sc-pnl-sub" data-i18n="lp.t5PnlSub">$900 from a single cascade · position closed in 4 minutes</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-tools"><span>d0 oi BTC</span><span>d0 derivatives</span><span>d0 fundingrate</span><span>d0 perps:order</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="story-card">
        <div class="sc-header">
          <span class="sc-type" data-i18n="lp.t6Type">YIELD ROTATION</span>
          <span class="sc-time">🔄 auto</span>
        </div>
        <p class="sc-story" data-i18n="lp.t6Story">D0 monitors DeFi yields daily. Drift APY dropped from 12% to 7.8%. Kamino launched a new vault at 14.2%. D0 auto-withdrew from Drift, deposited into Kamino. Zero downtime on capital.</p>
        <div class="sc-pnl-block gold">
          <div class="sc-pnl">+$180<span class="sc-pnl-unit">/mo</span></div>
          <div class="sc-pnl-sub" data-i18n="lp.t6PnlSub">extra yield from auto-rotation · 14.2% vs 7.8% APY</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-tools"><span>d0 drift:vaults</span><span>d0 kamino</span><span>d0 defi-yield</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="story-card">
        <div class="sc-header">
          <span class="sc-type" data-i18n="lp.t7Type">MM BEHAVIOR</span>
          <span class="sc-time">⏱ 2h</span>
        </div>
        <p class="sc-story" data-i18n="lp.t7Story">Asked D0: "Can I buy SOL now?" It ran market maker phase analysis — P5 accumulation detected, Setup Score 7.2/10. Entry zone $142-145, stop at $138. Entered at $143. MMs pushed price to $158 in 2 days.</p>
        <div class="sc-pnl-block green">
          <div class="sc-pnl">+10.5%</div>
          <div class="sc-pnl-sub" data-i18n="lp.t7PnlSub">followed MM accumulation phase · entered before markup</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-tools"><span>d0 mm-phase SOL</span><span>d0 setup-score</span><span>d0 orderflow</span><span>d0 perps:order</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="story-card">
        <div class="sc-header">
          <span class="sc-type" data-i18n="lp.t8Type">SHORT SQUEEZE</span>
          <span class="sc-time">⏱ 4h scan</span>
        </div>
        <p class="sc-story" data-i18n="lp.t8Story">D0's 4-hour scan flagged DOGE: funding rate at -0.08% (extreme negative), OI surging while price flat. Short squeeze setup confirmed. Went long with 3x. Shorts got liquidated — price rallied 22% in 6 hours.</p>
        <div class="sc-pnl-block green">
          <div class="sc-pnl">+$1,650</div>
          <div class="sc-pnl-sub" data-i18n="lp.t8PnlSub">caught short squeeze before it fired · 3x leveraged long</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-tools"><span>d0 fundingrate</span><span>d0 oi DOGE</span><span>d0 liquidations</span><span>d0 perps:order</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="story-card">
        <div class="sc-header">
          <span class="sc-type" data-i18n="lp.t9Type">TREND BREAKOUT</span>
          <span class="sc-time">⏱ 15min</span>
        </div>
        <p class="sc-story" data-i18n="lp.t9Story">D0 ran 4-dimensional breakout check on ETH: price above resistance ✓, volume 3.2x average ✓, futures OI confirming ✓, MA20/50/200 aligned ✓. All four passed. Entered long. ETH ran from $3,200 to $3,580.</p>
        <div class="sc-pnl-block green">
          <div class="sc-pnl">+11.8%</div>
          <div class="sc-pnl-sub" data-i18n="lp.t9PnlSub">4D breakout verification · no false breakout this time</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-tools"><span>d0 ta ETH</span><span>d0 volume</span><span>d0 oi ETH</span><span>d0 ma-alignment</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="story-card">
        <div class="sc-header">
          <span class="sc-type" data-i18n="lp.t10Type">GRID TRADING</span>
          <span class="sc-time">🔄 7 days</span>
        </div>
        <p class="sc-story" data-i18n="lp.t10Story">D0 detected BTC in range-bound mode: MA200 flat, ATR declining, Hurst index 0.42 (mean-reverting). Recommended grid: $82K-$88K, 12 levels. 7 days later: 94 fills, consistent small profits while others waited.</p>
        <div class="sc-pnl-block green">
          <div class="sc-pnl">+3.8%</div>
          <div class="sc-pnl-sub" data-i18n="lp.t10PnlSub">94 grid fills in 7 days · profit while market went sideways</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-tools"><span>d0 market-regime BTC</span><span>d0 grid-params</span><span>d0 perps:grid</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="story-card">
        <div class="sc-header">
          <span class="sc-type" data-i18n="lp.t11Type">PORTFOLIO CHECK</span>
          <span class="sc-time">⏱ 5min</span>
        </div>
        <p class="sc-story" data-i18n="lp.t11Story">"Check my portfolio." D0 scanned 8 holdings: BTC/ETH/SOL correlation at 0.94 — essentially the same bet 3x. Recommended: reduce SOL, add stablecoin yield position for uncorrelated returns. Rebalanced.</p>
        <div class="sc-pnl-block gold">
          <div class="sc-pnl">-38%<span class="sc-pnl-unit"> corr</span></div>
          <div class="sc-pnl-sub" data-i18n="lp.t11PnlSub">portfolio correlation dropped from 0.94 to 0.58 · real diversification</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-tools"><span>d0 portfolio</span><span>d0 correlation</span><span>d0 rebalance</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="story-card">
        <div class="sc-header">
          <span class="sc-type" data-i18n="lp.t12Type">MACRO PLAY</span>
          <span class="sc-time">⏱ 1 day</span>
        </div>
        <p class="sc-story" data-i18n="lp.t12Story">D0 flagged: DXY dropping + 10Y yield falling + oil stable = risk-on macro. BTC historically rallies 8-12% in this regime. Went long with tight stop. BTC moved from $84K to $91K in 5 days.</p>
        <div class="sc-pnl-block green">
          <div class="sc-pnl">+8.3%</div>
          <div class="sc-pnl-sub" data-i18n="lp.t12PnlSub">macro regime detection · DXY + yields + oil correlation signal</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-tools"><span>d0 macro</span><span>d0 dxy</span><span>d0 correlation</span><span>d0 perps:order</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ CAPABILITIES ═══ -->
<section class="lp-caps scroll-reveal">
  <div class="caps-inner">
    <div class="section-label" data-i18n="lp.capsLabel">WHAT IS D0</div>
    <h2 class="caps-headline" data-i18n="lp.capsHeadline">An AI trading agent you talk to.</h2>
    <p class="caps-sub" data-i18n="lp.capsSub">Four capabilities no human trader can match — every one backed by real trading data.</p>

    <div class="caps-grid">
      <div class="cap-card">
        <div class="cap-icon">💪</div>
        <h3 data-i18n="lp.cap1Title">Full-Stack Trader</h3>
        <p class="cap-hook" data-i18n="lp.cap1Hook">Analysis + execution + risk control. One agent replaces an entire trading team.</p>
        <p class="cap-proof" data-i18n="lp.cap1Proof">155 tools across 11 domains: research, perpetuals, DeFi, backtesting, prediction markets, on-chain analytics — all in one conversation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cap-card">
        <div class="cap-icon">⏰</div>
        <h3 data-i18n="lp.cap2Title">Never Sleeps</h3>
        <p class="cap-hook" data-i18n="lp.cap2Hook">3AM stop-loss execution. Weekend funding rate alerts. Holiday portfolio rebalance.</p>
        <p class="cap-proof" data-i18n="lp.cap2Proof">Crypto markets never close. D0 monitors 24/7 — you set the rules, it enforces them while you sleep.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cap-card">
        <div class="cap-icon">🧩</div>
        <h3 data-i18n="lp.cap3Title">Built-in Skills</h3>
        <p class="cap-hook" data-i18n="lp.cap3Hook">11 skill packs, all pre-loaded. No setup, no config — just ask and trade.</p>
        <p class="cap-proof" data-i18n="lp.cap3Proof">d0-perps for leverage, d0-defi for yield farming, d0-research for analysis — all 11 packs ready from day one. One agent, full coverage.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cap-card">
        <div class="cap-icon">🔒</div>
        <h3 data-i18n="lp.cap4Title">Hardcoded Discipline</h3>
        <p class="cap-hook" data-i18n="lp.cap4Hook">2% max loss. 30% position cap. 3-loss cool-down. Rules it refuses to break.</p>
        <p class="cap-proof" data-i18n="lp.cap4Proof">These aren't suggestions — they're red lines coded into D0's execution layer. No FOMO, no revenge trading, no "just this once."</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ SKILLS ═══ -->
<section class="lp-skills scroll-reveal">
  <div class="skills-inner">
